{"tid":844330,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【搬屋賣物】平放/免費 漫畫 設定集 周邊","createTime":"2018-10-01T19:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T13:24:38.000Z","uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aff9f1437019605e8fcea6ad68e48938debd24eb","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:32:30.000Z","msg":"交收最好係番九龍，免費嘅最好可以就吓時地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日會上倉再執嘢，應該仲有一堆figure同周邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢哋都搵到好主人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鋼鍊原畫展file 15$個有無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都知係冷門角難放，印象中仲有個係張梅<br />\n（如果有人放愛德/艾爾，我想收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抽唔到，好後悔無包盒）<br />\n下面係大家賞嚟，30$/個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/031209_b89012db2b42daaa711fa1b685ae80ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F031209_b89012db2b42daaa711fa1b685ae80ec.png&h=9577276e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/031243_21d878745aa9ea933aa03de34f3bd311.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F031243_21d878745aa9ea933aa03de34f3bd311.png&h=4fcce441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAB資料設定集，無睇過<br />\n但我唔記得本身有無特典<br />\n所以放住$80蚊本<br />\n貴咗/原來佢有特典嘅可以同我講番，會平番<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/031647_ca649fb6e26d01f859aea42d9c8479e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F031647_ca649fb6e26d01f859aea42d9c8479e1.png&h=d49df1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIm@s 8週年live場刊<br />\n無打開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> $80<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/032033_9f318d788717075000f6b345f51ba808.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F032033_9f318d788717075000f6b345f51ba808.png&h=bed34ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下免費<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/032701_ee3e56c57ffdbd9d5859d104566dbc96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F032701_ee3e56c57ffdbd9d5859d104566dbc96.png&h=0ea7fef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGBF Code已用，非常抱歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/032733_9cd5c7726493a94e72fe67d8524d9929.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F032733_9cd5c7726493a94e72fe67d8524d9929.png&h=fff5260b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/032804_a0a251ee3dff5f2d465d3825246fc3b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F032804_a0a251ee3dff5f2d465d3825246fc3b5.png&h=817a3e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8a75dbf169fde41d9f9354b723f41e34d22bf2a","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:36:32.000Z","msg":"唔記得放tg: Autumnorange<br />\n聽日再更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df798c7c0c063f1e6671c95ec27390f6470c6962","tid":844330,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"想知有咩figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca79e368bc006beb069e32a1c791ab76791690b4","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df798c7c0c063f1e6671c95ec27390f6470c6962","tid":844330,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"想知有咩figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"有3隻免費嘅 無盒 拆擺only 有塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要自己洗<br />\n分別係LL嘅Umi、K-ON!嘅梓喵同IM@S仙打女孩嘅凜<br />\n<br />\n有盒全新嘅有<br />\nMacross Delta一番賞嘅美雲<br />\n綾波麗 某一番賞<br />\nMacross F嘅クラン（盒唔靚）<br />\nIM@S嘅あずさ（盒唔靚）<br />\n其他我一時醒唔起，要聽日去睇睇<br />\n不過主要都係Eva/im@s/mf<br />\n以上都好似係景品，唔係貴嘢嚟<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾隻有盒全新、G.E.M出嘅銀魂/青驅/Reborn/黑執仲諗緊出唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係太捨得"},{"pid":"a3d97d6f3ffdc0c85bac43f261d99e6175f023a1","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T20:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">免費嘅最好可以就吓時地</span><br />\n其實呢句唔駛講，免費都多多聲氣嘅話就直接叫佢過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw竟然有im@s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec5febf21afc81dca8f26070f78bcbbbb08ef54","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d97d6f3ffdc0c85bac43f261d99e6175f023a1","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T20:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">免費嘅最好可以就吓時地</span><br />\n其實呢句唔駛講，免費都多多聲氣嘅話就直接叫佢過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw竟然有im@s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T22:09:52.000Z","msg":"因為真係有試過送嘢比人要就番佢地點唔係佢唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時因為覺得就咁掉咗好浪費所以真係老遠出去拎比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIm@s唔止本家同仙打 仲有百萬live呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係一番嚟"},{"pid":"b59304b781b3c43b7b846e942a0c3595b1414b9a","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec5febf21afc81dca8f26070f78bcbbbb08ef54","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d97d6f3ffdc0c85bac43f261d99e6175f023a1","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"