e-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F134923_7cefa51ef422feeef507832710bb3b88.png&h=100a217f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩隻rin都係買多收藏用嘅所以都係全新未開<br />\n500$/300$<br />\n唔知依家市價幾多，貴咗可以講番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面ranka自留C賞，因為太大個所以決定放咗B賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n200$"},{"pid":"26a3a3b5cd7f83c2795b4393848125a42cd30e95","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/140015_6466e59a0f45a2428225cfd39bcd9fe4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F140015_6466e59a0f45a2428225cfd39bcd9fe4.png&h=3a392473&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/140017_5d5a6754fe368c8afe97d36be721e60e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F140017_5d5a6754fe368c8afe97d36be721e60e.png&h=b96bbb34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩隻免費嘅<br />\n梓貓擺咗好耐，白T有少污糟同多塵要自己洗吓<br />\n凜個隻係一番嚟，抽到齊曬毛巾同杯先抽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後自己又買多隻新嘅，所以display呢隻就唔跟我搬啦<br />\n<br />\n留意番都無盒，僅display無丁過（都丁唔到）<br />\n因為始終擺過我都唔係幾好意思送人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但掉咗又覺得自己會落地獄，希望有人願意收留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54486e5ed02e7dca86bef7b2a49c622adb1fa941","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59304b781b3c43b7b846e942a0c3595b1414b9a","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec5febf21afc81dca8f26070f78bcbbbb08ef54","tid":844330,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d97d6f3ffdc0c85bac43f261d99e6175f023a1","tid":844330,"uid":37138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T20:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">免